itq:
Fishers in core companies are allocated up to 1/3 of the quotas of existing permanent licenses, but there is not a total percentage that they receive. Case studies in fisheries self-governance
Townsend, 2008
ieq:
Set number of quota/license holders. Case studies in fisheries self-governance
Townsend, 2008
iq:
TAC is distributed btw individual license holders and group license holders, the latter of whom can hold up to 1/3 of an individual license holder. Case studies in fisheries self-governance
Townsend, 2008
turf:
Groups can only have 3 of its members fishing within a 30 day period and 1 at any one time. Case studies in fisheries self-governance
Townsend, 2008.
Also Crab Fishing Areas 23 and 24 have limits on the number of traps that can be laid http://thenavigatormagazine.com/news/view_printer.asp?ID=350.
